ox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3L15 15M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><nav class=\"flex-1 space-y-8\" aria-label=\"Mobile navigation\"><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Shop</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/shop\">All Products</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-hoodie\">Heavyweight Hoodie</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-sweatpants\">Heavyweight Sweatpants</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Brand</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/about\">About KVRN</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/waitlist\">Waitlist</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Support</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/shipping-returns\">Shipping &amp; Returns</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/size-guide\">Size Guide</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></div></nav><div class=\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] flex gap-5 flex-shrink-0\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\">Instagram</a></div></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\" class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-[400] w-full max-w-[400px] bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex flex-col transition-transform duration-[550ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h2 class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase\">Bag</h2><button aria-label=\"Close bag\" class=\"p-2 -mr-2 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3l12 12M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full px-6 text-center gap-5\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Your bag is empty.</p><a href=\"/shop\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-transparent text-kvrn-text border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg active:bg-[#333333] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-10 px-5 text-[11px]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Browse collection</span></button></a></div></div></div><main id=\"main-content\"><div class=\"pt-[60px]\"><div class=\"kvrn-container section-y max-w-3xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-12\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] tracking-wide\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li class=\"text-[var(--color-text)]\" aria-current=\"page\">Shipping &amp; Returns</li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-[clamp(40px,6vw,72px)] font-light leading-none tracking-[-0.025em] mb-16\">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1><section class=\"mb-16\" aria-labelledby=\"shipping-h\"><h2 id=\"shipping-h\" class=\"kvrn-label mb-8\">Shipping</h2><div class=\"border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_80px_1fr] gap-2 md:gap-4 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">USA Standard</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">5–7 business days</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">$8</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Free on orders over $350</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_80px_1fr] gap-2 md:gap-4 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">USA Express</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">2–3 business days</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">$18</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"></p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_80px_1fr] gap-2 md:gap-4 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">Canada</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">7–10 business days</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">$22</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Import duties may apply</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_80px_1fr] gap-2 md:gap-4 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">Europe</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">7–12 business days</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">$28</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Import duties may apply</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_80px_1fr] gap-2 md:gap-4 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">Rest of World</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">10–20 business days</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">$35</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Import duties may apply</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-3 text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\"><p>Orders are typically processed within 1–2 business days, Monday through Friday. Tracking is included with every order.</p><p>International customers are responsible for any import duties or taxes levied by their local customs authority.</p></div></section><div class=\"kvrn-rule mb-16\"></div><section class=\"mb-16\" aria-labelledby=\"returns-h\"><h2 id=\"returns-h\" class=\"kvrn-label mb-8\">Returns</h2><p class=\"text-[16px] font-light mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-lg\">We accept returns within 30 days of delivery on unworn, unwashed items with original tags attached.</p><div class=\"space-y-0\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 py-7 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\"><span class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 w-5\">01</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-2\">Initiate your return</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Email hello@kvrn.com with your order number and the item(s) you wish to return. We respond within 24 hours.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 py-7 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\"><span class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 w-5\">02</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-2\">Receive your label</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">For US returns, we send a prepaid return label by email. International returns are at the customer&#x27;s expense unless the item is faulty.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 py-7 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\"><span class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 w-5\">03</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-2\">Drop it off</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Pack the item securely and attach the label. Drop off at any carrier location.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 py-7 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\"><span class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 w-5\">04</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-2\">Receive your refund</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Once we receive and inspect your return — typically 1–3 business days — your refund is processed to the original payment method within 5–10 business days.</p></div></div></div></section><div class=\"kvrn-rule mb-16\"></div><section aria-labelledby=\"conditions-h\"><h2 id=\"conditions-h\" class=\"kvrn-label mb-6\">Return conditions</h2><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-muted)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition with tags attached.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-muted)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Items showing signs of wear cannot be accepted.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-muted)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Original shipping cost is non-refundable.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-muted)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Faulty items are covered regardless of the return window. Contact us immediately.</li></ul></section><div class=\"mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Questions? Email<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-[var(--color-text)] underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\">hello@kvrn.com</a>. We respond within 24 hours.</p></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)]\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"kvrn-container\"><div class=\"py-16 md:py-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16\"><div class=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><a class=\"block text-[14px] font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-5\" href=\"/\">KVRN</a><p class=\"text-[13px] text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-[200px]\">Designed slowly.<br/>Built to remain.</p><div class=\"flex gap-5 mt-6\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-150\" aria-label=\"KVRN on Instagram\">Instagram</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label mb-5\">Shop</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-co